snippet.title: BlackThorne Keep Chronicles Official Alpha Gameplay Trailer - 2023
snippet.description:
We are proud to be sharing a little bit more of a very early build of our upcoming open word action RPG!

How far would you go to Rebuild your Legacy?

 Everything in this trailer is a Work in Progress!

Wishlist Now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2155320/BlackThorne_Keep__Chronicles/
Join our Discord: https://discord.com/invite/NDcK3Ys
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/blackthornekeep/
